Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.60,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:40.59,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Blundered Operation\Nat Loch Ness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful tone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:12.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your violin attracts even the fog.\NIt's begun to roll in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Fog? Tonight's a quiet and\Npeaceful London evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the fog\Nlaying over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:24.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is happening in London.\NWhat is wrong with this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do you mean the investigation\Ncame to a dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:38.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, it's not even a real painting.\NIt's just a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty would never deal with\Nthis kind of cheap stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Professor\Nwould never steal a replica?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:48.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least we can eliminate\None of our suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As you said,\Nthis is really a boring case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:56.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't you solve it for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:03:59.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A short while ago,\Nsomeone came here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He said three French\Nstudents are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:11.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just a cheap robbery case,\Nbut missing students as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! I'm busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:15.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Send him to somebody\Nwho is suitable for such a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:18.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The fog has gotten much heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you made London\Ninto a peaceful city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as\NSherlock Holmes is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:28.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,no criminal can commit\Nany crime in this big city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Even...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Professor Moriarty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:36.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The Professor is being quiet now,\Nbecause he is thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,another nasty plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See! We've got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you take this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We took the picture in Paris\Nbefore we went on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:06.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Three students of the Paris Art School\Nvanished while travelling in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:10.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have any acquaintances\Nin London, or in England?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:13.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, and they couldn't have\Nbeen able to go far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you receive anything\Nlike a threatening letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I didn't hear from\Nthem for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:22.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you start\Nlooking for them earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:31.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I have a cousin in Redding,\Nso I was travelling by myself for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So, when you went back\Nto your hotel three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,all your friends were gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even their luggage\Nwas unopened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand clearly.\NLet's investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:00.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How is everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:10.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the painting that\NI ordered coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning\Nto have us do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:18.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it will be finished soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The touch of the paint brush,\Nthe colour, and the way it's layered...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,even the way the light reflects...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,it's exactly like the\Npainting of Volgetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sell this for a\Nvery expensive price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very satisfied with\Nall of your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This would definitely add\Nsome class to my collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:42.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish that,\Nstart working on the next project.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!\NThat's not what you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You said this was the only one we had\Nto work on and that would be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?\NDo you want to go home quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't complain\Nand do your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish someone would find our message.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they might find this place\Nand come rescue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:18.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a long time since\NI last visited the National Gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:22.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Watson, we are not here\Nto appreciate the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So those three students came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:44.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody remembered them\Ncarefully sketching famous paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the next place we have to go to\Nis the Piccadilly auction centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:01.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:13.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lestrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:16.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:20.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Inspector! Is there anything\Ninteresting you found at Sotheby's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, are you investigating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:25.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,W... well, it's just a boring case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:28.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,People call me the finest\NInspector of Scotland Yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm being forced\Nto look for a replica painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Holmes,\Nwhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for some lost children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost children?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:39.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you're having some trouble,\NI'll be happy to assist you any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! We are gentlemen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen have to\Nbehave like gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to call me Colonel Moron.\NAnd, what is it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Moron,\NI saw Mr. Holmes over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,H... Holmes! Damn it! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't we supposed\Nto be gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley, what do I look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:26.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A veteran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!\NWe are gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes will never\Ndiscover who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We are gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:41.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey! You must be\NMr. Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:45.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are Doctor Watson. I'm always\Nreading your case report books.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse us. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The clues are coming together.\NLet's follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,525! 525!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,550!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The customer on my\Nleft side said 550!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,575!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,600!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,625!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, 625!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,650!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, 650!\NThe lady on my left said 650!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,670!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:20.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a bid of 670!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,700!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A bid of 700! 700! Will anybody\Nbid more than that? 700!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,720!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, 720!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,725!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,750!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a bid of 750!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anybody who\Nwants to offer more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,750! 750!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,800!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady on my left side said 800!\NDo I hear any more offers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. It has been sold for 800.\NCongratulations dear Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.\NI'm so glad. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!\NYou knocked that vase down for 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,800? Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:04.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, this place is\Nreally bustling with energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That means there are plenty\Nof rich people around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder crime\Nwill never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:11.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it will be the artwork of Volgetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:19.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It says many of the paintings\Nand sculptures were found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,in an old Scottish castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I can expect to see\Nsomething nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:32.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem! The next painting up for bid\Nnow is a very rare and valuable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:35.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was made during a bleak period\Nin art history. It survived through...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:39.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the Medieval wars, before it\Nfinally arrived, here, in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!\NWonderful! Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about this, but this is\Nthe first time I've ever seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that this kind of\Npainting is being auctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:55.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:12:01.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a marvellous piece of art,\Nit could be considered priceless! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:16.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the bidding for this wonderful\Npainting will start at 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:17.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,550!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:24.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A bid of 550! Is there anybody\Nwho wishes to bid more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,600!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:26.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,650!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,700!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,750!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a bid of 750!\NAre there any more bids?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:33.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,800!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,820!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,850!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,900!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,900! The bid for this painting\Nis now 900!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, I still think they're strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The two gentlemen who keep bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,950! Anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a valuable painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The value of this can't be\Ncompared to anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bid more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,M... Moriarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!\NAnd that painting is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:03.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A bid of 1550!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,1600!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,1650!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:11.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,1660!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,1665!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go up to 1700!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm! A bid of 1700!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats! He's gone too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, does anybody wish\Nto bid more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody else?\NDo I hear any more bids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:34.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The value of this painting\Nis much higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A... anybody else?\NA bid from anybody is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a little higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they should take\Nthe painting with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,1710!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:53.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It has been sold for\N1710 pounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:04.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I wanted to buy that painting\Nfrom the moment I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That painting I just bought is a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My 1710 pounds is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:28.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a landscape of Scotland\Ninside of an Italian painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A robbery of replicas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapped art students...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Scotland...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my money coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:52.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a telegraph for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:59.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Come to Kings Cross Station\Nas soon as possible. Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:02.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Telegraph for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:07.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:10.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I made Mr. Watson's favourite\Ncurry dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mr. Holmes can't make it either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where is Moriarty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Scotland?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll explain it to you\Non the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:34.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Moriarty stole the replica\Nand used it to make fake paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:40.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he kidnapped three art students\Nwho were visiting from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:43.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have imprisoned them\Nand forced them to forge paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:47.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.\NSo far, your explanation is logical, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:09.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful brightness!\NWhat a lovely tone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:13.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crime that can only be done\Nby one who understands art, as I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My active energy has no limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:18.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,People often get jealous\Nand try to destroy my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will never rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:23.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\Nare they still painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They are very submissive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I will make\Nthem paint Rembrandt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:31.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will express my dream to the world,\Nin light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where is the Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:43.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll catch up with us soon\Nalong with the local police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll bring too\Nmany officers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:55.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:00.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!\NStand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:02.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:03.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No! They're attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We've been too nice to them,\Nso they got puffed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:49.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash your face and\Ngo after them right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't work!\NNone of the keys match!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ram into the door together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:04.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:05.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very high!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:29.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Why don't you guys\Nchase them this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the faster\Nway to reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Charge and break in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:48.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lestrade!\NSmiley why don't you keep climbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back and tell the Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, there's so many police here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:02.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to load the\Ngold coins onto the Pteranodon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:02.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:03.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:06.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:08.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:09.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:10.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:11.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You are really slow!\NYou know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:21.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:26.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:28.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:32.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:35.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:51.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys seem like you're\Ncarrying very heavy luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I found them!\NDon't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! We have so\Nmany other escape routes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:09.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's him over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:13.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient!\NJust a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Ouch! Ouch!\NIt hurts! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:27.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on for a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't here.\NWhere did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:57.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, I'll give you credit\Nbecause you chased me this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:59.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you actually catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They tricked us!\NKeep chasing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:08.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:13.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:14.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:15.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave you alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley, jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!\NWe can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, jump! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:34.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Never let your hands go!\NPull them close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:37.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my gold coins!\NEven my replicas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:53.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:13.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave ho! Heave ho! Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:15.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The Inspector's\N"never give up" attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:18.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,and enthusiasm for his work\Nis so impressive, it exhausts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:19.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:24.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love a peaceful London,\Njust like you do, Mr. Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:26.52,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything underneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:28.53,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ness-ing" is there!
