Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:50.31,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitlers\NBRETT JACOBSEN, DIANA TOLIN,\NAKI MATSUMOTO & MAKOTO SHIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:24:00.28,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,During a strong wind that\Nwas blowing one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:03.82,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,the famous Rosetta Stone was stolen\Nfrom the Museum of Great Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:07.13,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,How could such a heavy stone\Nbeen carried out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:08.90,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,When Holmes was on the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:13.23,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,he visited a Japanese student\Nnamed Kinnosuke Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:18.13,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.13,0:24:22.84,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soseki Kite Battle\NOver London!
